    <title>Week3-7670</title>
    <link href="/posts/ff77d078.html"/>
    <url>/posts/ff77d078.html</url>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h1 id="week3---7670-大门">Week3 - 7670: 大门</h1><h2 id="前置知识差分">前置知识：差分</h2><h3 id="基础认识">基础认识:</h3><ul><li><p>差分是什么</p><p>可以简单理解为 是 <strong>前缀和</strong> 的逆运算</p></li><li><p>差分有什么用</p><p>通过维护差分序列的信息，实现多次区间修改。</p></li><li><p>差分的地位</p><p>同样是一种重要的预处理思想</p><p>注意：修改操作一定要在查询操作之前</p></li></ul><h3 id="一维差分">一维差分</h3><p>对于长度为 <span class="math inline"><em>n</em></span> 的数列 {<spanclass="math inline"><em>a</em><sub><em>i</em></sub></span>},如果要多次查询区间 <spanclass="math inline">[<em>l</em>, <em>r</em>]</span>的所有数字之和，就可以考虑使用前缀和。</p><h4 id="递推式">递推式</h4><p><span class="math display"><em>a</em><sub>0</sub> = 0</span></p><p><spanclass="math display"><em>d</em><em>i</em><em>f</em><sub><em>i</em></sub> = <em>a</em><sub><em>i</em></sub> − <em>a</em><sub><em>i</em> − 1</sub></span></p><p>其实 <span class="math inline"><em>a</em><sub><em>n</em></sub></span>就是 <spanclass="math inline"><em>d</em><em>i</em><em>f</em><sub><em>n</em></sub></span>的前缀和</p><h4 id="修改">修改</h4><p>现在假设我们需要修改 <spanclass="math inline">[<em>l</em>, <em>r</em>]</span>之间的数，对该区间所有数加上一个 <spanclass="math inline"><em>v</em><sub>0</sub></span></p><p>可以用下述语句来实现区间修改。</p><p><spanclass="math display"><em>d</em><em>i</em><em>f</em><sub><em>l</em></sub> + <em>v</em><sub>0</sub></span></p><p><spanclass="math display"><em>d</em><em>i</em><em>f</em><sub><em>r</em> + 1</sub> − <em>v</em><sub>0</sub></span></p><h4 id="举例">举例</h4><p>鉴于上面公式有点太抽象了，可能看不懂为什么要这么实现。</p><p>这里列个表你看了大概就知道了。</p><table><thead><tr><th>—</th><th>1</th><th>2</th><th>3</th><th>4</th><th>5</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td>a</td><td>1</td><td>3</td><td>2</td><td>5</td><td>7</td></tr><tr><td>dif</td><td>1</td><td>2</td><td>-1</td><td>3</td><td>2</td></tr><tr><td>sum</td><td>1</td><td>3</td><td>2</td><td>5</td><td>7</td></tr></tbody></table><p><span class="math inline"><em>a</em></span> 为<strong>原始数列</strong> ，<spanclass="math inline"><em>d</em><em>i</em><em>f</em></span> 为<strong>差分数列</strong> ，<spanclass="math inline"><em>s</em><em>u</em><em>m</em></span> 为<strong>差分数列</strong> 的 <strong>前缀和</strong>，显然发现 <spanclass="math inline"><em>s</em><em>u</em><em>m</em> = <em>a</em></span></p><p>现在假设我要对 <span class="math inline">[2, 4]</span>区间上每一个数加上 <span class="math inline">2</span></p><table><thead><tr><th>—</th><th>1</th><th>2</th><th>3</th><th>4</th><th>5</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td>a</td><td>1</td><td>3</td><td>2</td><td>5</td><td>7</td></tr><tr><td>dif</td><td>0</td><td>2</td><td>0</td><td>0</td><td>-2</td></tr><tr><td>sum</td><td>0</td><td>2</td><td>2</td><td>2</td><td>0</td></tr><tr><td>b</td><td>1</td><td>5</td><td>4</td><td>7</td><td>7</td></tr></tbody></table><p>这里具体计算公式如下</p><p><spanclass="math display"><em>s</em><em>u</em><em>m</em><sub><em>i</em></sub> = <em>s</em><em>u</em><em>m</em><sub><em>i</em> − 1</sub> + <em>d</em><em>i</em><em>f</em><sub><em>i</em></sub></span><spanclass="math display"><em>b</em><sub><em>i</em></sub> = <em>a</em><sub><em>i</em></sub> + <em>s</em><em>u</em><em>m</em><sub><em>i</em></sub></span></p><p>发现了吗？我们对 <spanclass="math inline"><em>d</em><em>i</em><em>f</em></span> 修改后，再对<span class="math inline"><em>d</em><em>i</em><em>f</em></span> 进行一遍<strong>前缀和</strong> 计算就能得到修改后的 <strong>新数组</strong><span class="math inline"><em>b</em></span></p><h4 id="对比">对比</h4><p>因此，我们便可以在 <span class="math inline"><em>O</em>(1)</span>的时间修改区间 <span class="math inline">[<em>l</em>, <em>r</em>]</span>的所有数字，代价是我们需要 <spanclass="math inline"><em>O</em>(<em>n</em>)</span>的时间求解差分的逆运算（前缀和），来获得修改后的数组。</p><p>示例：对于 <span class="math inline"><em>m</em></span> 个区间修改<span class="math inline">[<em>l</em>, <em>r</em>]</span>。</p><p>如果采用暴力算法，对每个区间进行遍历加上 <spanclass="math inline"><em>v</em><sub>0</sub></span> ，时间复杂度为 <spanclass="math inline"><em>O</em>(<em>m</em> * <em>n</em>)</span></p><p>但是用差分优化查询，时间复杂度为 <spanclass="math inline"><em>O</em>(<em>m</em> + <em>n</em>)</span></p><p>这么对比能大概 get 到差分的用途了吗？</p><blockquote><p>这里看不懂 <span class="math inline"><em>O</em>(...)</span>是什么可以留个概念，有这么个玩意，等之后老师讲，或者直接问学长。</p></blockquote><h2 id="具体思路">具体思路</h2><p>上面解释了 <strong>差分</strong>的基础知识。相信你已经对这道题有了一定的思路了。</p><p>假如你因为不了解 <strong>差分</strong>而写不出来，可以暂停阅读，想一想 <strong>差分</strong>应该怎么应用到这道题上。</p><p>如果还是没什么思路，就跟着我下面的来看看这道题。</p><h3 id="题意分析">题意分析</h3><p>题目给了我们 <span class="math inline"><em>n</em></span>个门，每个门可以被 <spanclass="math inline">[<em>l</em>, <em>r</em>]</span>上的钥匙打开，最后求有几把钥匙，可以打开 <spanclass="math inline"><em>k</em></span> 个门。</p><p>假设 <spanclass="math inline"><em>k</em><em>e</em><em>y</em>[<em>i</em>]</span>为第 <span class="math inline"><em>i</em></span>把钥匙能打开多少扇门。</p><p>也就是我们要求出所有 <spanclass="math inline"><em>k</em><em>e</em><em>y</em>[<em>i</em>]</span>大于 <span class="math inline"><em>k</em></span> 的个数</p><p><spanclass="math display"><em>Σ</em>(<em>k</em><em>e</em><em>y</em>[<em>i</em>] ≥ <em>k</em>)</span></p><p>注意到要 <strong>区间修改</strong></p><h3 id="最直观的想法暴力">最直观的想法，暴力</h3><p>简单来说，我们可以对每一组区间进行暴力修改，从而得到每个门能被几把钥匙打开。</p><figure class="highlight cpp"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs cpp"><span class="hljs-keyword">for</span>( <span class="hljs-type">int</span> i = <span class="hljs-number">1</span>; i &lt;= m; ++ i ) <br>&#123;<br>    <span class="hljs-type">int</span> left = <span class="hljs-number">0</span>, right = <span class="hljs-number">0</span>;<br>    <span class="hljs-built_in">scanf</span>(<span class="hljs-string">&quot;%d%d&quot;</span>, &amp;left, &amp;right);<br>    <span class="hljs-keyword">for</span>( <span class="hljs-type">int</span> j = left; j &lt;= right; ++ j ) &#123;<br>        key[j] ++;<br>    &#125;<br>&#125;<br><span class="hljs-type">int</span> cnt = <span class="hljs-number">0</span>;<br><span class="hljs-keyword">for</span>( <span class="hljs-type">int</span> i = <span class="hljs-number">1</span>; i &lt;= n; ++ i ) <br>&#123;<br>    <span class="hljs-keyword">if</span>( key[i] &gt;= k ) &#123;<br>        cnt ++;<br>    &#125;<br>&#125;<br><span class="hljs-built_in">printf</span>(<span class="hljs-string">&quot;%d&quot;</span>, cnt);<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>但是这种写法无疑会暴力运算每一个区间，最终的时间复杂度为 <spanclass="math inline"><em>O</em>(<em>n</em><sup>2</sup>)</span>。</p><p>对于这题 <span class="math inline"><em>n</em> ≤ 1<em>e</em>5</span>来说，最终时间为 <span class="math inline">1<em>e</em>10</span> 超过了<span class="math inline">1<em>s</em></span> 时间限制的 <spanclass="math inline">1<em>e</em>8</span> 的数据处理量。</p><blockquote><p><span class="math inline">1<em>e</em>5 = 10<sup>5</sup></span>科学技术法 方便书写</p><p>一般来说，计算机 <span class="math inline">1<em>s</em></span> 能执行<span class="math inline">1<em>e</em>8</span> 的数据处理。</p><p>所以对于输入数据的规模，我们需要找到不同时间复杂度的算法来解决问题。</p><p>这就是算法的应用，你理解了吗？</p></blockquote><p>因此，我们需要一个更加优秀的算法解决这个问题。</p><h3 id="不难想到的优化差分">不难想到的优化，差分</h3><p>根据之前对题目的分析，我们发现，其实我们每次对 <spanclass="math inline">[1, <em>j</em>]</span> 以及 <spanclass="math inline">[<em>j</em> + 1, <em>n</em>]</span>两个区间的修改。</p><p>占据了很多时间，而这种区间修改，我们则可以使用差分来优化。</p><p>不难想到：对于区间 <spanclass="math inline">[<em>l</em>, <em>r</em>]</span> 的区间所有值 <spanclass="math inline">+1</span> ，只需要如下两个算式;</p><p><spanclass="math display"><em>d</em><em>i</em><em>f</em>[<em>l</em>] + 1</span><spanclass="math display"><em>d</em><em>i</em><em>f</em>[<em>r</em> + 1] − 1</span></p><p>所以如果我们对区间进行修改，每次只需要用两个算式修改 <spanclass="math inline"><em>d</em><em>i</em><em>f</em></span>差分数组就行，不用每个点修改过去，</p><p>这样的话，时间复杂度就是 <spanclass="math inline"><em>O</em>(<em>n</em> * 2)</span>。</p><p>因为复杂度可以消去常数，所以理论上就是 <spanclass="math inline"><em>O</em>(<em>n</em>)</span>。</p><p>对于这道 <span class="math inline">1<em>e</em>5</span> 的 <spanclass="math inline"><em>n</em></span> ，完全足以胜任。</p><p>以下是代码实现</p><figure class="highlight cpp"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs cpp"><span class="hljs-keyword">for</span>( <span class="hljs-type">int</span> i = <span class="hljs-number">1</span>; i &lt;= n; ++ +i ) &#123;<br>    <span class="hljs-type">int</span> l, r;<br>    <span class="hljs-built_in">scanf</span>(<span class="hljs-string">&quot;%d%d&quot;</span>, &amp;l, &amp;r);<br>    dif[l] ++;<br>    dif[r<span class="hljs-number">+1</span>] --;<br>&#125;<br><br><span class="hljs-type">int</span> cnt = <span class="hljs-number">0</span>;<br><span class="hljs-keyword">for</span>( <span class="hljs-type">int</span> i = <span class="hljs-number">1</span>; i &lt;= m; ++ i ) &#123;<br>    sum[i] = sum[i<span class="hljs-number">-1</span>] + dif[i];<br>    b[i] = a[i] + sum[i];<br>    <span class="hljs-keyword">if</span>( b[i] &gt;= k ) &#123;<br>        cnt ++;<br>    &#125;  <br>&#125;<br><span class="hljs-built_in">printf</span>(<span class="hljs-string">&quot;%d\n&quot;</span>, cnt );<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="不过这题还没结束">不过这题还没结束</h3><p>如果使用 <spanclass="math inline"><em>s</em><em>u</em><em>m</em></span> 和 <spanclass="math inline"><em>b</em></span>数组，会让代码变得冗余。这里给出一个修改优化方案。</p><p>直接计算当前位置的 <spanclass="math inline"><em>s</em><em>u</em><em>m</em></span>，因为 <spanclass="math inline"><em>s</em><em>u</em><em>m</em></span>的修改只取决于上一个值，而且不需要重复利用，所以可以这么写。</p><p>最后给出ac代码</p><figure class="highlight cpp"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br><span class="line">20</span><br><span class="line">21</span><br><span class="line">22</span><br><span class="line">23</span><br><span class="line">24</span><br><span class="line">25</span><br><span class="line">26</span><br><span class="line">27</span><br><span class="line">28</span><br><span class="line">29</span><br><span class="line">30</span><br><span class="line">31</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs cpp"><span class="hljs-meta">#<span class="hljs-keyword">include</span><span class="hljs-string">&lt;bits/stdc++.h&gt;</span></span><br><span class="hljs-keyword">using</span> <span class="hljs-keyword">namespace</span> std;<br><br><span class="hljs-type">const</span> <span class="hljs-type">int</span> maxn = <span class="hljs-number">1e5</span> + <span class="hljs-number">50</span>;<br><br><span class="hljs-type">long</span> <span class="hljs-type">long</span> key[maxn];<br><span class="hljs-type">long</span> <span class="hljs-type">long</span> dif[maxn];<br><br><span class="hljs-function"><span class="hljs-type">int</span> <span class="hljs-title">main</span><span class="hljs-params">()</span> </span>&#123;<br>    <span class="hljs-type">int</span> n, m, k;<br>    <span class="hljs-built_in">scanf</span>(<span class="hljs-string">&quot;%d%d%d&quot;</span>, &amp;n, &amp;m, &amp;k);<br><br>    <span class="hljs-keyword">for</span>( <span class="hljs-type">int</span> i = <span class="hljs-number">1</span>; i &lt;= n; ++ i ) &#123;<br>        <span class="hljs-type">int</span> l, r;<br>        <span class="hljs-built_in">scanf</span>(<span class="hljs-string">&quot;%d%d&quot;</span>, &amp;l, &amp;r);<br>        dif[l] ++;<br>        dif[r<span class="hljs-number">+1</span>] --;<br>    &#125;<br><br>    <span class="hljs-type">int</span> sum = <span class="hljs-number">0</span>;<br>    <span class="hljs-type">int</span> cnt = <span class="hljs-number">0</span>;<br>    <span class="hljs-keyword">for</span>( <span class="hljs-type">int</span> i = <span class="hljs-number">1</span>; i &lt;= m; ++ i ) &#123;<br>        sum += dif[i];<br>        <span class="hljs-keyword">if</span>( key[i] + sum &gt;= k ) &#123;<br>            cnt ++;<br>        &#125;  <br>    &#125;<br><br>    <span class="hljs-built_in">printf</span>(<span class="hljs-string">&quot;%d\n&quot;</span>, cnt );<br>    <span class="hljs-keyword">return</span> <span class="hljs-number">0</span>;<br>&#125;<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="结语">结语</h2><p>很感谢你能看到这里，愿你在 ac过程中不断成长，每一次提交都能学到一点新东西。</p>]]></content>
    
    
    
